command_msg_s Struct Reference


Data Fields

cmd_type_e cmd
int param
int size

Detailed Description

This structure defines the command/responce message structure.

Field Documentation

cmd_type_e cmd

Command message type.

int param

Message parameter.

int size

Size of data message that follows the command message. If size is 0 no data message is sent.
